{"id": "lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0001", "text": "也許這個理由不便形容你未夠膽講", "structure": {"line_index": 1, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 9, 5, 4, 5, 0, 3, 2, 0, 0, 5, 2, 4, 9, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jaa5", "heoi2", "ze5", "go3", "lei5", "jau4", "bat1", "bin6", "jing4", "jung4", "nei5", "mei6", "gau3", "daam2", "gong2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "也許", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這個", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "理由", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不便", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "形容", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "未夠", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "膽", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "講", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "假使我漂亮", "artists": ["關心妍"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1056", "prev_line_id": null, "next_line_id": "lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0002", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0002", "text": "也許不愛我只因藐視我未能似藝人好看", "structure": {"line_index": 2, "char_count": 17}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 9, 3, 4, 5, 9, 3, 5, 2, 5, 2, 0, 5, 2, 0, 9, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jaa5", "heoi2", "bat1", "oi3", "ngo5", "zi2", "jan1", "miu5", "si6", "ngo5", "mei6", "nang4", "ci5", "ngai6", "jan4", "hou2", "hon3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "也許", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不愛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "只", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "因", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "藐視", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "未能", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "似", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "藝人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "好看", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "假使我漂亮", "artists": ["關心妍"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1056", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0001", "next_line_id": "lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0003", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0003", "text": "原諒我 未發現情人爲外貌這麼嚮往", "structure": {"line_index": 3, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 2, 5, 2, 4, 2, 0, 0, 2, 2, 5, 3, 4, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jyun4", "loeng6", "ngo5", "mei6", "faat3", "jin6", "cing4", "jan4", "ngoi6", "maau6", "ze5", "mo1", "hoeng3", "wong5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "原諒", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "未", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "發現", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "情人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "爲", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "外貌", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這麼", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "嚮往", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "假使我漂亮", "artists": ["關心妍"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1056", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0002", "next_line_id": "lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0004", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0004", "text": "而你竟疏遠全沒有情講", "structure": {"line_index": 4, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 5, 9, 3, 5, 0, 2, 5, 0, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ji4", "nei5", "ging2", "so1", "jyun5", "cyun4", "mut6", "jau5", "cing4", "gong2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "而", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "竟", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "疏遠", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "全", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "情講", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "假使我漂亮", "artists": ["關心妍"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1056", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0003", "next_line_id": "lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0005", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0005", "text": "假使我漂亮 性格縱使不喫香 如明星賣相", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 17}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [9, 9, 5, 3, 2, 4, 4, 4, 9, 3, 4, 3, 0, 0, 3, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["gaa2", "si2", "ngo5", "piu1", "loeng6", "sing3", "gaak3", "zung3", "si2", "bat1", "hek3", "hoeng1", "jyu4", "ming4", "sing1", "maai6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "假使", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "漂亮", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "性格", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "縱使", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "喫香", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "如", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "明星", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "賣相", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "假使我漂亮", "artists": ["關心妍"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1056", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0006", "text": "亦惹來讚賞 得到這種對象 纏綿才馨香", "structure": {"line_index": 6, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 5, 0, 4, 9, 3, 4, 5, 9, 4, 2, 0, 0, 0, 3, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jik6", "je5", "loi4", "zaan3", "soeng2", "dak1", "dou3", "ze5", "zung2", "deoi3", "zoeng6", "cin4", "min4", "coi4", "hing1", "hoeng1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "亦", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "惹", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "來", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "讚賞", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "得到", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這種", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "對象", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "纏綿", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "才", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "馨香", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "假使我漂亮", "artists": ["關心妍"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1056", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0005", "next_line_id": "lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0007", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0007", "text": "多幾個對象 怕你愛得比我傷 有另一下場", "structure": {"line_index": 7, "char_count": 17}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 9, 4, 4, 2, 4, 5, 4, 3, 9, 5, 3, 5, 2, 3, 2, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["do1", "gei2", "go3", "deoi3", "zoeng6", "paa3", "nei5", "oi3", "dak1", "bei2", "ngo5", "soeng1", "jau5", "ling6", "jat1", "haa6", "coeng4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "多", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "幾個", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "對象", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "怕", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "得", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "比", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "傷", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "另", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一下場", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "假使我漂亮", "artists": ["關心妍"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1056", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0006", "next_line_id": "lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0008", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0008", "text": "但愛情沒價 何必幻想", "structure": {"line_index": 8, "char_count": 9}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 4, 0, 2, 4, 0, 3, 2, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["daan6", "oi3", "cing4", "mut6", "gaa3", "ho4", "bit1", "waan6", "soeng2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "但", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愛情", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒價", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "何必", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "幻想", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "假使我漂亮", "artists": ["關心妍"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1056", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0007", "next_line_id": "lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0009", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
